<lb n="0862b02" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0862b03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0862b04" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 64 [No. 26(122)]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0862b05" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說瞻婆比丘經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0862b06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0862b07" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉<note n="0862002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏法師＝沙門釋【三】</note><note n="0862002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三藏法師【大】，沙門釋【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862002"><lem wit="【大】">三藏法師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沙門釋</rdg></app>法炬譯</byline>
<lb n="0862b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT01p0862b0801">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT01p0862b0804" rend="inline">一時，婆伽婆在瞻婆恒伽<note n="0862003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝卜【三】</note><note n="0862003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，卜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862003"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">卜</rdg></app>法賴池
<lb n="0862b09" ed="T"/>水上。彼時，世尊十五日說戒，在比丘僧前坐。
<lb n="0862b10" ed="T"/>世尊坐已，觀諸比丘意之所念。觀諸比丘意
<lb n="0862b11" ed="T"/>之所念已，夜初一分時坐默然住。於是，有異
<lb n="0862b12" ed="T"/>比丘從<note n="0862004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【三】</note><note n="0862004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐【大】，座【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862004"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">座</rdg></app>起，一<note n="0862005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">向＝面【三】</note><note n="0862005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">向【大】，面【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862005"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">面</rdg></app>著衣，叉手向世尊，白世尊
<lb n="0862b13" ed="T"/>曰：「<note n="0862006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】＊</note><note n="0862006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】＊，惟【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>，世尊！夜一時已過，世尊及比丘僧坐已
<lb n="0862b14" ed="T"/>久，<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>願世尊，當說戒。」彼時，世尊默然住。世
<lb n="0862b15" ed="T"/>尊至夜半默然坐住，彼比丘再叉手向世尊，
<lb n="0862b16" ed="T"/>白世尊曰：「<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>，世尊！夜已過初時，夜已過半。
<lb n="0862b17" ed="T"/>世尊！比丘僧坐已久，<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>願世尊，當說戒。」彼
<lb n="0862b18" ed="T"/>時世尊亦默然住。彼時世尊於夜半後坐默
<lb n="0862b19" ed="T"/>然住，彼比丘三叉手向世尊，白世尊曰：「<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>
<lb n="0862b20" ed="T"/><note n="0862007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔願〕－【三】</note><note n="0862007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862007"><lem wit="【大】">願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>世尊，夜已過初時，夜已過半，夜已過半
<lb n="0862b21" ed="T"/>後明星欲出，不久當明星出。世尊！比丘僧坐
<lb n="0862b22" ed="T"/>已久，<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>願世尊，當說戒。」彼時，世尊告此比
<lb n="0862b23" ed="T"/>丘曰：「我比丘眾中有不淨者。」</p><p xml:id="pT01p0862b2312" rend="inline">彼時尊者大目
<lb n="0862b24" ed="T"/><note n="0862008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乾＝揵【三】＊</note><note n="0862008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾【大】＊，揵【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連亦在眾中會，眾中會已，於是尊者大目
<lb n="0862b25" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連作是念：「世尊為說何比丘？言眾中有不
<lb n="0862b26" ed="T"/>淨。我寧可作如<note n="0862009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝是【三】</note><note n="0862009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862009"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">是</rdg></app>像三昧正受，以三昧意，
<lb n="0862b27" ed="T"/>觀諸比丘意之所念。」於是尊者大目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連，即
<lb n="0862b28" ed="T"/>如其像三昧正受，以三昧意觀諸比丘意之
<lb n="0862b29" ed="T"/>所念。尊者大目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連即便知之，世尊所為比
<pb n="0862c" ed="T" xml:id="T01.0064.0862c"/>
<lb n="0862c01" ed="T"/>丘。於是尊者大目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連從三昧起，便至彼比
<lb n="0862c02" ed="T"/>丘所，到已牽彼比丘臂將出門外：「汝愚人去！
<lb n="0862c03" ed="T"/>汝不應在此宿，無有比丘共汝住者，汝今
<lb n="0862c04" ed="T"/>為比丘外。」於是尊者大目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連牽彼比丘
<lb n="0862c05" ed="T"/>臂將出門外，反閉門，<note n="0862010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閉＝關【三】</note><note n="0862010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閉【大】，關【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0862010"><lem wit="【大】">閉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">關</rdg></app>門已，至世尊所，
<lb n="0862c06" ed="T"/>到已禮世尊足，却坐一面。尊者大目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連
<lb n="0862c07" ed="T"/>却一面已，白世尊曰：「世尊！所說比丘者，言
<lb n="0862c08" ed="T"/>眾中有不淨，我已牽彼比丘臂將出門外。『汝
<lb n="0862c09" ed="T"/>愚人去，汝不應在此宿，無有比丘共住汝，今
<lb n="0862c10" ed="T"/>比丘為是外。』<app type="star" corresp="#0862006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>世尊！已過夜初分，已過夜
<lb n="0862c11" ed="T"/>半，已過夜半後，夜已欲曉明星出時，明星
<lb n="0862c12" ed="T"/>不久當出。世尊！比丘僧坐已久，願世尊，
<lb n="0862c13" ed="T"/>當說戒。」</p><p xml:id="pT01p0862c1304" rend="inline">「汝目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！彼愚癡人為多受罪，
<lb n="0862c14" ed="T"/>而觸嬈世尊及比丘僧。若目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！眾中有
<lb n="0862c15" ed="T"/>不淨比丘，如來說戒者，彼愚人頭當破為七
<lb n="0862c16" ed="T"/>分。是故汝，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！從今日始，汝等當共說
<lb n="0862c17" ed="T"/>戒，如來不復來說戒。何以故？目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！此
<lb n="0862c18" ed="T"/>一愚人如是過已，過觀而觀屈<note n="0862011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">申＝伸【三】＊</note><note n="0862011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">申【大】＊，伸【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0862011"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">伸</rdg></app>卷舒，持
<lb n="0862c19" ed="T"/>僧伽梨衣鉢，而於他梵行者自言是梵行。
<lb n="0862c20" ed="T"/>此目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！若人言是梵行者，若人作是念：
<lb n="0862c21" ed="T"/>『沙門為幻，沙門為麤，沙門為刺，沙門非言。』如
<lb n="0862c22" ed="T"/>是知已，便棄著外。何以故？恐壞餘淨比丘故。
<lb n="0862c23" ed="T"/>猶若，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！成就稻田麥田，若中有惡草
<lb n="0862c24" ed="T"/>生，彼草根如麥根，枝節葉實亦如是，未成其
<lb n="0862c25" ed="T"/>子當棄之。目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！若成子已，彼田居士便
<lb n="0862c26" ed="T"/>作是念：『此為是壞麥子之草，麥之刺、麥之麤。』
<lb n="0862c27" ed="T"/>彼便拔，棄著外。何以故？恐壞餘淨麥故。如是，
<lb n="0862c28" ed="T"/>目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！若有一愚人作是念過已，過觀而觀
<lb n="0862c29" ed="T"/>屈<app type="star" corresp="#0862011"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">伸</rdg></app>卷舒，持僧伽梨衣鉢，而於餘梵行者自
<pb n="0863a" ed="T" xml:id="T01.0064.0863a"/>
<lb n="0863a01" ed="T"/>言是梵行者。若，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！他稱言是梵行者，
<lb n="0863a02" ed="T"/>彼若作是念：『此沙門壞，此沙門<note n="0863a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">刺【CB】，剌【大】</note><app n="0863a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">刺</lem><rdg wit="【大】">剌</rdg></app>，此沙門麤，
<lb n="0863a03" ed="T"/>此沙門非言。』彼知已，便棄著外。何以故？恐壞
<lb n="0863a04" ed="T"/>餘淨比丘故。猶若，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！彼田居士，於冬
<lb n="0863a05" ed="T"/>月時治大穀<note n="0863001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">積＝𧂐【三】</note><note n="0863001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">積【大】，𧂐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0863001"><lem wit="【大】">積</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">𧂐</rdg></app>，若彼穀所有<note n="0863a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">堅【CB】【麗-CB】，竪【大】</note><app n="0863a0501"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">堅<note type="cf1">K19n0679_p0540c23</note><note type="cf2">X23n0438_p0385a12</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">竪</rdg></app>
固住者，一向
<lb n="0863a06" ed="T"/>皆離去，謂所有若草若葉，彼揚著風中一向
<lb n="0863a07" ed="T"/>吹去，彼田居士，執掃<g ref="#CB00416"/>在中<note n="0863002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是…過觀＝掃之在中掃令淨何以故恐壞餘淨【元】【明】</note><note n="0863002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是目乾連若愚人作是行過已過觀【大】，掃之在中掃令淨何以故恐壞餘淨【元】【明】</note><app n="0863002"><lem wit="【大】">是。目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">揵</rdg></app><!--saywhat：原本[＊]來源[0862008]校勘是「乾＝揵【三】＊」，但因【元】【明】與[0863002]校勘造成版本重複的問題，因此此處[＊]版本直接刪除了【元】【明】，未經查證。-->連！若
<lb n="0863a08" ed="T"/>愚人作是行過已，過觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">掃之在中掃令淨何以故恐壞餘淨</rdg></app>穀故。如是，目乾連！若
<lb n="0863a09" ed="T"/>一愚人，作是行過已，過觀而觀屈<app type="star" corresp="#0862011"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">伸</rdg></app>卷舒，持
<lb n="0863a10" ed="T"/>僧伽梨衣鉢，而於他梵行者，自言是梵行者。
<lb n="0863a11" ed="T"/>若，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！他稱是梵行者，他作是念：『此沙門
<lb n="0863a12" ed="T"/>壞，此沙門麤，此沙門刺。』彼知已，棄著外。何以
<lb n="0863a13" ed="T"/>故？恐壞餘比丘故。猶，目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！彼田居士，彼
<lb n="0863a14" ed="T"/>求水欲通水，執極利斧入於林中，彼執斧<note n="0863003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">㭬＝<g ref="#CB04811"/>【三】</note><note n="0863003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">㭬【大】，<g ref="#CB04811"/>【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0863003"><lem wit="【大】">㭬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><g ref="#CB04811"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0863a15" ed="T"/>樹，謂彼所有樹堅固住而不可入。謂<note n="0863004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所有＝有所【明】</note><note n="0863004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所有【大】，有所【明】</note><app n="0863004"><lem wit="【大】">所有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">有所</rdg></app>枯
<lb n="0863a16" ed="T"/>樹打已斧則陷入。田居士截其根，<note n="0863a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">截【CB】，載【大】</note><app n="0863a1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">截</lem><rdg wit="【大】">載</rdg></app>根已通
<lb n="0863a17" ed="T"/>其中，通其中已便作木筧凾通水。如是。目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>
<lb n="0863a18" ed="T"/>連！或一愚人作如是行過已，過觀而觀屈<app type="star" corresp="#0862011"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">伸</rdg></app>
<lb n="0863a19" ed="T"/>卷舒。持僧伽梨衣鉢，而於他梵行者，<note n="0863005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝目【明】</note><note n="0863005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，目【明】</note><app n="0863005"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">目</rdg></app>言是
<lb n="0863a20" ed="T"/>梵行者。若。目<app type="star" corresp="#0862008"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">揵</rdg></app>連！他稱言是梵行者，彼
<lb n="0863a21" ed="T"/>作是念：『沙門壞，沙門麤，沙門刺，沙門非。』
<lb n="0863a22" ed="T"/>彼知已，棄著外。何以故？恐壞餘淨比丘故。說
<lb n="0863a23" ed="T"/>偈<note n="0863006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝言【三】</note><note n="0863006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】，言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0863006"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">言</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0863a24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT01p0863a2401" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「共止及當知，</l><l>惡求及瞋恚，</l>
<lb n="0863a25" ed="T"/><l>恚恨不捨貪，</l><l>不棄幻諛諂。</l>
<lb n="0863a26" ed="T"/><l><note n="0863007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莊＝在【三】</note><note n="0863007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莊【大】，在【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0863007"><lem wit="【大】">莊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">在</rdg></app>人詐言息，</l><l>自說是沙門，</l>
<lb n="0863a27" ed="T"/><l>自作諸惡行，</l><l>惡見非是樂。</l>
<lb n="0863a28" ed="T"/><l>多作諸妄言，</l><l>如是知彼已，</l>
<lb n="0863a29" ed="T"/><l>悉皆不與會，</l><l>擯棄不共止。</l>
<pb n="0863b" ed="T" xml:id="T01.0064.0863b"/>
<lb n="0863b01" ed="T"/><l>知時<note n="0863008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝俱【明】</note><note n="0863008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具【大】，俱【明】</note><app n="0863008"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">俱</rdg></app>淨行，</l><l>分別誰言已，</l>
<lb n="0863b02" ed="T"/><l>非息言沙門，</l><l>惡行擯棄已。</l>
<lb n="0863b03" ed="T"/><l>不與惡共止，</l><l>數數及日日，</l>
<lb n="0863b04" ed="T"/><l>悉皆共<note n="0863009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">集會＝會集【三】</note><note n="0863009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">集會【大】，會集【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0863009"><lem wit="【大】">集會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">會集</rdg></app>，</l><l>當棄此苦際。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0863b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT01p0863b0501">佛如是說，彼諸比丘聞世尊所說，歡喜而樂。</p>
<lb n="0863b06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說瞻婆比丘經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>